description:
Hear your music the simple way: stored on your phone, ready to play, no WiFi required. Offline Music Player is a clean, focused audio player made for people who keep their tracks as files and just want a reliable way to listen. Pick the songs and folders you want with an easy file picker, then press play and enjoy. No accounts, no streaming, no noise. Just your music.

From your downloaded songs to complete music folders, Offline Music Player lets you enjoy your tracks with smooth and reliable playback. Open the app, select the songs or folders you want, and start listening instantly. Use classic music controls—play, pause, next, previous, shuffle, and repeat—to shape your listening flow wherever you are. Whether you’re on a flight, commuting, or simply trying to stay offline, all your music plays seamlessly because everything is stored directly on your device.

The design puts clarity first: large buttons, a minimal layout, and a distraction-free now playing screen keep you focused on what you’re hearing, not what you’re tapping. You can keep the music going in the background while you chat, browse, or lock your phone, and control playback from the notification shade or lock screen for quick access. Lightweight and battery-friendly, Offline Music Player is built to stay out of the way and let your audio take center stage.

What you can do:
- Play offline audio: Listen to local music and sound files with no internet or data usage.
- Manual file selection: Choose the songs and folders you want with a simple file picker.
- Simple playlists: Group tracks into listening sessions that match your mood or activity.
- Classic controls: Use play, pause, next, previous, shuffle, and repeat to control playback.
- Background listening: Keep your music running while you use other apps or lock your phone.
- Lightweight experience: Enjoy smooth performance without heavy battery drain or bloat.

Style, clarity, and control in one:
- Minimal interface: Clean, focused design with no unnecessary menus or distractions.
- Instant start: Open the app, pick your files, and start listening right away.
- Fully offline: No streaming, no sign-ups, and no uploads—your audio stays on your device.
- Privacy by default: Everything plays locally, so your listening habits remain yours alone.

Note: Offline Music Player is a local audio player. It does not search the internet, download songs, or stream from online music services. It plays only the files you select from your device.

ALL THE MUST-HAVE DJ TOOLS

- pitch control and key lock

- set the vinyl inertia, and the starting speed of the vinyl
